[7HD Channel]

7
00:00:15,740 --> 00:00:18,700
[IQIYI]

8
00:00:21,700 --> 00:00:26,140
♫ I’m just someone, who isn’t that perfect ♫

9
00:00:26,140 --> 00:00:32,500
♫ But for you, I’m willing to give it all ♫

10
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:36,740
♫ Whether you’d love me, or care about me or not ♫

11
00:00:36,740 --> 00:00:42,260
♫ That’s for you to decide, but as for me I’m… ♫

12
00:00:42,260 --> 00:00:44,780
♫ (Will be right here) not going anywhere ♫

13
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:47,380
♫ (Hold my hand) stay by my side ♫

14
00:00:47,380 --> 00:00:52,300
♫ Just turn around and you’ll see ♫

15
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:56,300
♫ You’ll always have me by your side ♫

16
00:00:56,300 --> 00:00:58,860
♫ In this marriage that our love will last forever♫

17
00:00:58,860 --> 00:01:04,300
♫ I promise I’ll give you all my heart♫

18
00:01:04,300 --> 00:01:07,140
♫ Remember when I said…♫

19
00:01:07,140 --> 00:01:12,220
♫ That I’ll take great care of you♫

20
00:01:12,220 --> 00:01:20,740
♫ I promise those words will always stay true♫

21
00:01:20,740 --> 00:01:23,260
[Marriage on Earth]

22
00:01:25,700 --> 00:01:27,420
[Previously]
[Din]: I’m sorry I bothered you.

23
00:01:27,730 --> 00:01:29,560
[Rose]: I’ll go see Din and apologise to her about last night.

24
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:34,130
[Rose]: All this time, I care about you a lot and get very possessive of you.

25
00:01:34,220 --> 00:01:36,860
[Rose]: Now, I’ve finally realised…

26
00:01:36,860 --> 00:01:37,930
[Kaew]: Are you okay, Miss?

27
00:01:38,060 --> 00:01:38,930
Are you hurt anywhere?

28
00:01:38,930 --> 00:01:41,060
[Moddang: Even a wife like you isn’t that worried, Miss.

29
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:42,660
[Din]: Are you still mad at me?

30
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:46,580
[Din]: If you don’t say anything, I’ll take it as a no.

31
00:01:46,900 --> 00:01:48,729
[Din]: I’ve liked you for a long time.

32
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:54,180
[Moddang]: They said Mr. Wasupol and his son are behind human trafficking.

33
00:01:54,180 --> 00:01:56,940
[Moddang]: They’ve been taken in for interrogation at the police station.

34
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,200
[Rose]: Mr. Wasupol has hired a hitman?

35
00:01:58,460 --> 00:01:59,729
[Rose]: Din, look out!

36
00:02:01,060 --> 00:02:01,860
[Rose]: Din!

37
00:02:04,140 --> 00:02:05,780
Rose…

38
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:16,220
I love you, Din. I love you. Do you hear me?

39
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:31,940
Din!

40
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:35,800
Din!

41
00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:37,860
Please call the ambulance!

42
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:47,160
Hello? Someone got shot!

43
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,760
Please come quick! In front of Chiang Rai hotel!

44
00:02:53,300 --> 00:02:54,340
Din…

45
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:26,100
Doctor, how’s Din?

46
00:03:26,530 --> 00:03:28,820
The bullet missed the patient’s vital organs.

47
00:03:29,579 --> 00:03:31,860
She’s over the critical stage now.

48
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:34,340
But I still have to keep her under close monitoring.

49
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,100
Thank you very much, Doctor.

50
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,200
Okay, on my way there.

51
00:04:05,460 --> 00:04:08,200
It was you, wasn’t it? You sent someone to shoot Miss Din.

52
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:12,260
Calm down, will you?

53
00:04:12,700 --> 00:04:14,060
We’re on the same boat anyway.

54
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,580
Who’s on the same boat with you?

55
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:18,540
You didn’t keep your word and hurt her.

56
00:04:18,730 --> 00:04:20,899
Our deal is over.

57
00:04:21,529 --> 00:04:24,260
I’m not going to tip you off on anything about Saen Rak farm again.

58
00:04:24,730 --> 00:04:26,620
You think you can quit so easily?

59
00:04:31,730 --> 00:04:36,180
Don’t you think I have our conversations recorded every time you tell me about them?

60
00:04:38,100 --> 00:04:43,700
Think about it. If you work with me, she’ll be yours in the end.

61
00:05:17,100 --> 00:05:18,060
Din.

62
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:22,460
Din.

63
00:05:34,900 --> 00:05:36,330
Rose.

64
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:45,600
Why are you crying?

65
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:55,580
I’m just happy. I thought I’d never hear your voice again.

66
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:05,540
I miss you. Do you hear me?

67
00:06:06,660 --> 00:06:07,460
Yes.

68
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,620
[Lom]: I miss you too.

69
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:23,220
Geez, how long have you been here?

70
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:26,780
We’ve been sitting here for ages.

71
00:06:27,380 --> 00:06:31,420
I guess this is why they said love can make you blind.

72
00:06:31,420 --> 00:06:33,900
You can’t see anyone in this room but her!

73
00:06:33,930 --> 00:06:38,700
Yeah. I used to get shot too. It was really nothing.

74
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:41,940
You’re only whining to get her attention, aren’t you?

75
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,900
Did you say it was nothing?

76
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:50,140
You know what, that time when I went to visit her…

77
00:06:53,659 --> 00:06:56,620
[Lom]: Quiet. Shush.
[Fai]: Help me, Din!

78
00:06:56,860 --> 00:06:58,140
[Moddang]: Miss Rose!

79
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:05,300
Miss Rose! Mr. Thipakorn…He finally came to!

80
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:35,380
Congratulations. The patient is responding now.

81
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:38,020
Thank you, Doctor. Thank you.

82
00:07:39,060 --> 00:07:40,180
Thank you!

83
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,400
Dad!

84
00:07:48,130 --> 00:07:48,930
Dad!

85
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:03,100
You don’t have to say anything, Dad.

86
00:08:05,820 --> 00:08:07,460
Please rest.

87
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,100
I’ll be right here.

88
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,580
Please don’t cry.

89
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,260
Don’t cry.

90
00:08:40,929 --> 00:08:43,100
I’ll come check on your wound again tomorrow.

91
00:08:43,530 --> 00:08:44,330
Thank you.

92
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:50,700
There, there. You’re safe now.

93
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:02,530
Miss, are you all right? Does it hurt a lot?

94
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:07,130
I’m fine, Kaew. I should be discharged in a few days.

95
00:09:09,060 --> 00:09:11,400
I came right away after Dad told me what happened.

96
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:18,860
Weren’t you also there with Din yesterday?

97
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:22,500
How come you only knew about it now?

98
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:25,620
Yesterday, Miss Din told me to go get the car.

99
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:28,260
By the time I drove out, I couldn’t see her anywhere.

100
00:09:28,620 --> 00:09:30,660
I tried calling her but it didn’t go through.

101
00:09:31,780 --> 00:09:35,180
So, I decided to drive back to the farm and heard about what happened from Dad.

102
00:09:40,700 --> 00:09:44,780
Anyway, where’s Miss Rose? I thought she’d be here to care for Miss Din.

103
00:09:45,460 --> 00:09:48,300
[Fai]: She’s with Mr. Thipakorn. His condition is getting…

104
00:09:48,300 --> 00:09:49,860
[Din]: Not so good.

105
00:09:58,930 --> 00:10:01,400
Do you want to eat anything? I’ll go buy it for you.

106
00:10:03,660 --> 00:10:05,860
Maybe you should let her wife take care of that.

107
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:09,260
She’ll be back soon.

108
00:10:12,340 --> 00:10:13,340
Okay.

109
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:18,360
I’m not hungry, Kaew.

110
00:10:20,130 --> 00:10:25,200
So, does anyone at our farm know I got shot?

111
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:31,560
Only some of them. Dad hardly told anyone. He’s afraid they might be worried.

112
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:40,180
Please look after the farm for me then.

113
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:44,300
Yes, Miss. Please get well soon.

114
00:10:45,130 --> 00:10:46,360
I’ll be home soon.

115
00:10:57,130 --> 00:10:58,400
I miss our bedroom so bad.

116
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,960
Then, stay here and take lots of rest.

117
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:07,300
Don’t go to work. Stay here until you’re fully recovered.

118
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,980
And let me take care of you.

119
00:11:23,330 --> 00:11:26,820
I’m sorry you have to go through all this because of me.

120
00:11:27,260 --> 00:11:30,020
Instead of dedicating all your time to take care of Uncle Thip…

121
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:32,740
Now, you have to care for me too.

122
00:11:34,060 --> 00:11:37,020
Please don’t say that. I’m willing to do it.

123
00:11:39,020 --> 00:11:40,620
So sweet.

124
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:45,820
About Uncle Thip gaining consciousness,

125
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:48,540
can you please not tell anyone yet?

126
00:11:49,620 --> 00:11:53,580
Let’s keep it between us, Moddang, and my cousins.

127
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:56,300
Why?

128
00:12:01,060 --> 00:12:03,900
Someone on our farm is secretly working for Wasu.

129
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:10,460
I fear if this information leaks out, Uncle Thip might be in danger.

130
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:19,860
Okay, I’ll be careful. I’ll tell Moddang to keep it a secret too.

131
00:12:22,130 --> 00:12:23,340
Thank you.

132
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,220
Here’s the vegetable.

133
00:12:40,660 --> 00:12:43,020
Thank you, Miss Rose.

134
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:45,860
Please make Din her favourite dish tonight, Aunt Chan.

135
00:12:46,420 --> 00:12:49,300
She said she misses your cooking the most.

136
00:12:50,260 --> 00:12:55,980
Wow! Then I guess I’ll have to pour all my heart into it.

137
00:12:58,730 --> 00:12:59,730
[Moddang]: Miss Rose.

138
00:13:01,100 --> 00:13:02,860
[Moddang]: Miss Kaew is here to see Miss Din.

139
00:13:03,060 --> 00:13:05,780
I already told her Miss Din is sleeping but she refuses to leave.

140
00:13:05,780 --> 00:13:06,980
She said she’ll wait.

141
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,380
She’s waiting at the entrance.

142
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:14,620
Should we go and confront her now? I’m so ready!

143
00:13:41,260 --> 00:13:43,660
You can leave your message with me.

144
00:13:44,260 --> 00:13:47,820
Din is probably sleeping right now and won’t be able to come see her guest.

145
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:49,700
Never mind then.

146
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:52,900
I can wait here until she wakes up.

147
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:57,060
But I don’t know when she’ll be up.

148
00:13:57,060 --> 00:13:59,860
I can wait. My house is just around the corner.

149
00:14:03,380 --> 00:14:06,060
Geez! Impossibly shameless.

150
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:18,700
Hello, Miss.

151
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:22,200
What’s the matter, Kaew?

152
00:14:24,330 --> 00:14:27,060
Please don’t go. Stay here with me.

153
00:14:28,860 --> 00:14:29,660
Don’t go anywhere.

154
00:14:34,930 --> 00:14:39,660
I’m here to check on you. And to report you on what you’ve asked me to look into.

155
00:14:41,130 --> 00:14:42,620
But…

156
00:14:45,300 --> 00:14:49,660
I don’t keep any secrets from my wife. You can just say it.

157
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:53,740
Maybe I should have it confirmed first.

158
00:14:53,740 --> 00:14:55,940
I’ll come back and tell you later then.

159
00:14:58,760 --> 00:15:02,260
But then, wouldn’t it be a waste for you to come all the way here?

160
00:15:04,100 --> 00:15:09,820
Not at all. I’d need her signature on this document anyway.

161
00:15:14,140 --> 00:15:15,420
Let me help.

162
00:15:26,530 --> 00:15:28,000
Please get well soon, Miss.

163
00:15:31,660 --> 00:15:33,020
Thank you, Kaew.

164
00:15:34,460 --> 00:15:38,380
Well, I suppose I should get going then.

165
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:56,660
Let’s go inside.

166
00:16:18,460 --> 00:16:22,980
Hold on. I have something to talk to you.

167
00:16:38,260 --> 00:16:39,460
Are you sulking?

168
00:16:40,380 --> 00:16:41,660
No, I’m not.

169
00:16:46,730 --> 00:16:49,760
I swear Kaew and I are really just friends.

170
00:16:53,380 --> 00:16:56,180
I know. I trust you.

171
00:16:57,200 --> 00:17:03,300
But whenever I see her getting close to you, I can’t help but get jealous.

172
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:06,599
But I like it though.

173
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:10,579
Very much.

174
00:17:13,760 --> 00:17:15,540
Don’t try to sweet talk me.

175
00:17:16,730 --> 00:17:19,260
I’m trying to control my jealousy here.

176
00:17:22,760 --> 00:17:25,940
Do you want me to help? I have an idea.

177
00:17:27,060 --> 00:17:28,740
What is it?

178
00:18:24,530 --> 00:18:26,060
I…I’m sorry.

179
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:31,200
Are you feeling better now?

180
00:18:34,900 --> 00:18:40,100
From now on, if you get jealous again, I’ll use this trick.

181
00:18:43,260 --> 00:18:49,300
Then, I’ll get jealous over everything–be it the wind, the sky, or even the air.

182
00:20:05,360 --> 00:20:07,020
[Kla]: Mr. Kasidit.

183
00:20:13,130 --> 00:20:14,620
[Kla]: Say hello to him.

184
00:20:15,530 --> 00:20:16,700
[Kaew]: Hello.

185
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:19,860
You’re Kaew, right?

186
00:20:20,220 --> 00:20:23,580
From now on, think of Saen Rak farm as your own home.

187
00:20:23,900 --> 00:20:27,260
And don't worry about your education. I’ll take care of everything.

188
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:31,300
You should go to the same school as Din, so that you two can be friends.

189
00:20:50,560 --> 00:20:53,160
Miss, can you please help me with this part?

190
00:20:54,360 --> 00:20:55,660
Let me see.

191
00:20:57,860 --> 00:21:03,820
Oh, this? There’re 5 levels of leadership. They’re…

192
00:21:15,020 --> 00:21:20,100
[Saen Rak Farm Office]

193
00:21:25,600 --> 00:21:28,260
I’ve summarized today’s lecture for you, Miss.

194
00:21:28,860 --> 00:21:31,820
But the professor said you can’t skip any more classes.

195
00:21:32,930 --> 00:21:35,960
Thanks a lot, Kaew. Without you, I would've been in so much trouble.

196
00:21:37,700 --> 00:21:41,900
No problem, Miss. If there’s anything I could help, you can always let me know.

197
00:21:42,130 --> 00:21:42,930
Thanks.

198
00:22:06,300 --> 00:22:08,180
You’ve harboured your crush for a long time.

199
00:22:09,300 --> 00:22:11,700
But in her eyes, you're just nobody.

200
00:22:13,620 --> 00:22:16,500
In the end, she chose to share her bed with someone else.

201
00:22:20,100 --> 00:22:21,500
Shut up.

202
00:22:23,800 --> 00:22:25,900
Don't you want her back?

203
00:23:12,160 --> 00:23:16,060
Mr. Wasu, I’ve made up my mind.

204
00:23:28,730 --> 00:23:30,020
[Rose]: Your snacks are here.

205
00:23:34,330 --> 00:23:36,860
[Fai]: Sis, you’ll go to Chiang Mai tomorrow, right?

206
00:23:36,930 --> 00:23:38,260
Want me to go with you?

207
00:23:39,100 --> 00:23:40,180
No need.

208
00:23:41,760 --> 00:23:43,980
You’re going to Chiang Mai again?

209
00:23:45,330 --> 00:23:46,620
Can you not go?

210
00:23:48,730 --> 00:23:49,800
I have to, Rose.

211
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:54,140
It’s a very important job. I already postponed it once.

212
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:56,780
But I’m afraid you might get ambushed again.

213
00:23:59,360 --> 00:24:04,060
I’ll be careful. And it’s not just me and Kaew alone.

214
00:24:04,360 --> 00:24:07,340
Lom will also send two bodyguards to keep watch over me.

215
00:24:10,980 --> 00:24:12,340
Please don’t worry.

216
00:24:16,700 --> 00:24:18,620
Am I still needed here?

217
00:24:23,900 --> 00:24:25,260
Like there were only the two of you.

218
00:24:26,600 --> 00:24:29,820
Just eat your strawberry. Is it good?

219
00:24:30,600 --> 00:24:31,900
So sweet.

220
00:24:31,900 --> 00:24:33,620
Have some more.

221
00:24:47,100 --> 00:24:49,380
Miss Din will go to Chiang Mai tomorrow.

222
00:24:49,380 --> 00:24:51,820
And Lieutenant Wayo will not be at the farm.

223
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:54,540
We should hurry and get on with our plan.

224
00:24:54,860 --> 00:24:59,340
Good. I’ll send my men to get rid of those bodyguards.

225
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:03,300
What you have to do is use that brat to lure Rose out.

226
00:25:03,540 --> 00:25:08,340
Fine. But remember, don’t you dare lay a finger on Miss Din.

227
00:25:08,860 --> 00:25:16,580
Agreed. You can have that brat. As for Rose, she’s mine.

228
00:25:43,600 --> 00:25:46,260
I’ll stop by a bit to grab some coffee, Miss.

229
00:25:47,100 --> 00:25:48,020
Sure.

230
00:25:48,660 --> 00:25:50,060
Do you need anything?

231
00:25:51,660 --> 00:25:52,730
As usual is fine.

232
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:54,000
Okay.

233
00:26:21,760 --> 00:26:24,300
Your coffee, Miss. Be careful, it’s hot.

234
00:26:24,300 --> 00:26:25,380
Thanks.

235
00:26:25,530 --> 00:26:27,560
I’ll go give these to the cops first.

236
00:27:09,700 --> 00:27:13,100
You can take some rest, Miss. I’ll wake you up when we get there.

237
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:15,100
[Police]: What’s wrong with your car?

238
00:28:46,530 --> 00:28:48,140
Is there something wrong, Miss?

239
00:28:50,360 --> 00:28:55,580
It’s Din. She still hasn’t read or replied to my messages.

240
00:28:56,730 --> 00:29:01,130
Aww, you two have only been apart for a few hours, are you missing her now?

241
00:29:03,400 --> 00:29:05,260
Is this time to tease me?

242
00:29:24,930 --> 00:29:27,260
Why isn’t she picking up?

243
00:29:30,980 --> 00:29:34,180
[A call getting cut off]

244
00:29:37,580 --> 00:29:39,540
["Have a safe trip. Please take care.", "Are you there yet?"
"Where are you now?, "Why so quiet? Are you okay?"]

245
00:29:43,020 --> 00:29:46,100
[Incoming call: Din]

246
00:29:49,130 --> 00:29:50,260
Miss Kaew!

247
00:29:53,100 --> 00:29:54,300
Surprised, aren’t you?

248
00:29:56,100 --> 00:29:57,100
What’s going on?

249
00:29:58,960 --> 00:30:01,730
It’s pretty obvious. How can you still not get it?

250
00:30:13,260 --> 00:30:14,530
Let me tell you something,

251
00:30:15,400 --> 00:30:21,460
if she really loves you, she wouldn’t have enjoyed sleeping with me behind your back like this.

252
00:30:22,460 --> 00:30:23,700
I don’t believe you!

253
00:30:23,800 --> 00:30:25,930
That work in Chiang Mai is only an excuse…

254
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:29,020
for me and her to spend a pleasant time together.

255
00:30:30,260 --> 00:30:31,940
See it for yourself.

256
00:30:37,100 --> 00:30:40,820
No! Don’t do anything to her!

257
00:30:41,500 --> 00:30:43,660
Din! Din!

258
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,300
Din!

259
00:31:13,330 --> 00:31:15,380
Moddang, can’t you go any faster?

260
00:31:15,380 --> 00:31:16,860
Yes, Miss!

261
00:31:27,060 --> 00:31:28,220
Hey!

262
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:29,780
[Wasu’s men]: Get out of the car!

263
00:31:30,380 --> 00:31:31,180
Get out now!

264
00:31:31,180 --> 00:31:33,540
[Wasu’s men]: Get out!
- [Moddang & Rose]: No! Get off me!

265
00:31:33,540 --> 00:31:35,460
[Moddang & Rose]: Get off me!

266
00:31:36,740 --> 00:31:37,860
[Wasu’s men]: Do you wanna die?!

267
00:31:37,940 --> 00:31:39,700
[Moddang & Rose]: Get off me!

268
00:31:40,700 --> 00:31:43,580
[Moddang]: Miss Rose! Miss Rose! Don’t do anything to her!

269
00:31:43,580 --> 00:31:44,420
Let’s go!

270
00:31:44,420 --> 00:31:46,580
[Moddang]: Miss Rose! Miss Rose!

271
00:31:46,700 --> 00:31:48,180
[Wasu’s men]: Hurry up!
[Moddang]: Miss Rose!

272
00:31:48,180 --> 00:31:49,340
[Moddang]: Miss Rose!

273
00:32:02,700 --> 00:32:06,460
Mr. Wasu, have your men taken care of the rest?

274
00:32:07,260 --> 00:32:11,340
We’ve got her now. You did a great job.

275
00:32:37,700 --> 00:32:43,140
Miss, do you know how much I love you?

276
00:32:57,960 --> 00:32:59,180
Miss Din!

277
00:32:59,460 --> 00:33:01,180
You’re working for Wasu, aren’t you?

278
00:33:04,860 --> 00:33:05,660
No.

279
00:33:08,060 --> 00:33:10,020
Wasu…made me do this.

280
00:33:10,530 --> 00:33:13,700
Kaew that I used to know would never let anyone manipulate her so easily.

281
00:33:13,700 --> 00:33:16,860
But everything that I did, I did it because I love you.

282
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:20,260
I’ve loved you first, long before she came.

283
00:33:21,100 --> 00:33:24,460
All this time, do you really think I don’t know how you feel about me?

284
00:33:27,360 --> 00:33:32,730
I’ve always made it clear, whether through my words or actions, that you’re just a friend to me.

285
00:33:41,130 --> 00:33:46,220
I’ve pretended like I didn’t know because I don’t want to lose a friend like you.

286
00:33:55,260 --> 00:34:00,700
I’m begging you, Kaew. Please don’t do this.

287
00:34:02,160 --> 00:34:05,860
I don’t want to see my best friend making the wrong choice.

288
00:34:12,330 --> 00:34:17,340
Do you know…what’s more painful than getting attacked by your enemy?

289
00:34:19,460 --> 00:34:21,940
It’s getting betrayed by someone you trust.

290
00:35:35,460 --> 00:35:38,300
Rose! What are you doing?

291
00:35:41,060 --> 00:35:42,020
[Rose]: Get off me!

292
00:35:42,580 --> 00:35:44,860
Let me go!

293
00:35:45,220 --> 00:35:46,140
Get off me!

294
00:35:46,540 --> 00:35:47,420
Let me go!

295
00:35:47,420 --> 00:35:49,460
- Rose!
- Get off me!

296
00:35:51,700 --> 00:35:52,780
What the fuck?!

297
00:35:53,100 --> 00:35:55,340
[Moddang]: You’re done. I’ve recorded everything.

298
00:35:55,340 --> 00:35:57,180
What the hell are you doing?

299
00:35:57,500 --> 00:35:58,500
Are you all right, Miss?

300
00:35:59,100 --> 00:36:00,620
What the fuck are you doing?

301
00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:02,800
[Police]: Freeze!

302
00:36:03,100 --> 00:36:03,900
What the fuck?!

303
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:11,220
[Lom]: We’ve solid evidence and even an eye witness. You won’t get away this time.

304
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:13,300
Did you fucking set me up?

305
00:36:13,900 --> 00:36:18,140
Smart ass. We've found out long ago that Kaew works for you.

306
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:22,100
[Kaew]: Your coffee, Miss. I'll give these to the cops first.

307
00:36:29,060 --> 00:36:30,420
I bought you guys some coffee.

308
00:36:30,700 --> 00:36:31,940
[Police]: Thank you, Miss.
- Thank you.

309
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:32,800
[Kaew]: Be careful, it’s hot.

310
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:33,740
[Police]: Yes.

311
00:36:33,740 --> 00:36:36,700
[Kaew]: If I’m not wrong, this one is Americano. And this one is black coffee.

312
00:36:36,900 --> 00:36:38,620
[Police]: Thank you, Miss. We really need them right now.

313
00:36:38,730 --> 00:36:39,530
[Kaew]: My pleasure.

314
00:36:58,460 --> 00:37:00,740
[Moddang]: Miss Rose! Miss Rose!

315
00:37:20,220 --> 00:37:22,980
[Wasu’s men]: Get out! Move!

316
00:37:24,660 --> 00:37:25,260
Go!

317
00:37:30,060 --> 00:37:31,020
[Lom]: Freeze!

318
00:37:39,860 --> 00:37:44,340
If it weren’t for Kaew, I wouldn’t have been able to catch you red-handed like this.

319
00:37:44,340 --> 00:37:45,460
You set me up!

320
00:37:46,780 --> 00:37:48,100
[Police]: Don’t move! Sit down!

321
00:37:48,100 --> 00:37:50,420
[Police]: Sit!
[Wasu]: Get off me!

322
00:37:50,420 --> 00:37:51,340
Handcuff him!

323
00:37:51,340 --> 00:37:52,220
What the fuck?!

324
00:37:53,860 --> 00:37:56,820
I said get off me! Let me go!

325
00:37:58,540 --> 00:37:59,980
You, fucking bitch!

326
00:38:04,100 --> 00:38:05,500
Are you hurt anywhere, Miss?

327
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:06,900
Are you all right?

328
00:38:06,900 --> 00:38:08,100
I’m fine.

329
00:38:09,730 --> 00:38:10,960
Are you okay, Rose?

330
00:38:11,900 --> 00:38:12,760
I’m okay.

331
00:38:13,160 --> 00:38:15,560
I’ll get someone to drop you off at the safehouse.

332
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:19,020
Moddang, come with me to the police station to give your statement first.

333
00:38:19,500 --> 00:38:21,900
Yes, Miss. Thank you.

334
00:38:22,100 --> 00:38:22,900
Thank you.

335
00:38:26,580 --> 00:38:27,980
Are you all right, Moddang?

336
00:38:27,980 --> 00:38:28,780
I’m all right, Miss.

337
00:38:33,660 --> 00:38:35,220
Thank you, Moddang.

338
00:38:52,700 --> 00:38:54,020
Din!

339
00:38:55,700 --> 00:38:56,660
Rose!

340
00:38:57,460 --> 00:39:00,100
Din!

341
00:39:06,700 --> 00:39:13,580
♫All the ups and downs we’ve been through together♫

342
00:39:13,580 --> 00:39:20,100
♫Those things made my heart begin to flutter♫

343
00:39:20,100 --> 00:39:25,580
♫Everytime when you look at me♫

344
00:39:25,580 --> 00:39:30,300
♫Do you know it makes me imagine things?♫

345
00:39:30,300 --> 00:39:32,540
Rose, how are you?

346
00:39:32,540 --> 00:39:35,140
Are you all right? Are you hurt anywhere

347
00:39:36,260 --> 00:39:38,260
Lom told me you were so brave.

348
00:39:39,800 --> 00:39:42,420
I’m okay. I’m good now.

349
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:45,600
Promise me you won’t put yourself in danger like that again.

350
00:39:46,860 --> 00:39:49,660
I’m sorry I didn't tell you first.

351
00:39:50,900 --> 00:39:54,500
How did you know Miss Kaew is the mole?

352
00:39:55,180 --> 00:39:57,580
Lom started to suspect Kaew after I got shot.

353
00:39:57,820 --> 00:40:01,700
She sent someone to follow her and found out about her plan.

354
00:40:04,330 --> 00:40:06,200
What did you do to Miss Kaew after that?

355
00:40:14,930 --> 00:40:15,730
Sis!

356
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:20,900
Are you all right?

357
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:24,600
I’m fine.

358
00:40:26,130 --> 00:40:30,940
Lom just called. She said Wasu has been arrested. Things are going according to plan.

359
00:40:33,460 --> 00:40:36,700
As for you, get ready for a raft of charges.

360
00:40:36,700 --> 00:40:41,060
Kidnapping, holding someone against her will, and even working for the trafficking criminal like Wasu.

361
00:40:44,960 --> 00:40:46,060
Well, I…

362
00:40:49,730 --> 00:40:50,960
I’m not going to report her to the police.

363
00:40:52,100 --> 00:40:53,180
What?!

364
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:55,500
Are you crazy?

365
00:40:55,730 --> 00:40:58,360
She committed a crime. She should be taken in for interrogation.

366
00:41:03,160 --> 00:41:08,300
It was my fault too. I was the cause that made her do this.

367
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:14,800
I want to give her a chance.

368
00:41:25,400 --> 00:41:32,340
Miss Din, I’m so sorry.

369
00:41:34,060 --> 00:41:40,420
I don’t think I can forgive you for what you did.

370
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:46,260
But I will not hurt you the same way you hurt me.

371
00:41:51,500 --> 00:41:55,780
From now on, I’m no longer your friend.

372
00:41:56,100 --> 00:41:59,460
And Saen Rak farm is never again a home to you.

373
00:42:29,530 --> 00:42:31,160
How are you feeling then?

374
00:42:35,530 --> 00:42:37,000
Kaew is my best friend.

375
00:42:40,200 --> 00:42:41,540
She’s like a family to me.

376
00:42:45,330 --> 00:42:49,980
To be betrayed by her like that,

377
00:42:58,060 --> 00:42:59,700
I’m…I’m really at a loss for words.

378
00:44:28,800 --> 00:44:31,060
I already asked our lawyer to take care of this case.

379
00:44:35,330 --> 00:44:37,220
Just you wait, Bitch.

380
00:44:37,600 --> 00:44:41,340
I’ll come kick your ass once I’m off the hook.

381
00:44:41,360 --> 00:44:46,380
Sorry, can’t wait. I’m a cop, not your lady in waiting.

382
00:44:46,730 --> 00:44:48,820
- You, fucking…!!
- [Wasupol]: Stop causing trouble!

383
00:44:49,730 --> 00:44:51,980
Haven’t you shamed us enough already?

384
00:44:53,000 --> 00:44:55,660
But she trapped me, Dad! It was all her plan!

385
00:44:56,260 --> 00:44:58,600
Wanna add one more charge for insulting an official?

386
00:44:59,060 --> 00:44:59,700
Wasu!

387
00:45:05,560 --> 00:45:06,620
Let’s go home.

388
00:45:25,660 --> 00:45:27,820
He didn’t shift the blame to Miss Kaew?

389
00:45:28,530 --> 00:45:29,330
No, sir.

390
00:45:52,660 --> 00:45:55,000
Hey, what are you doing?

391
00:45:58,360 --> 00:46:01,260
I’m deleting pictures of you that Miss Kaew sent me.

392
00:46:04,930 --> 00:46:07,960
You’re quite good at acting, do you know that?

393
00:46:09,530 --> 00:46:12,220
Look, you seemed to enjoy it.

394
00:46:14,060 --> 00:46:16,580
Well, I had to do my best to make her believe.

395
00:46:16,660 --> 00:46:20,820
Otherwise, she wouldn’t have let slip that she works for Wasu.

396
00:46:23,260 --> 00:46:28,140
So, you had to let her hug you, kiss you, and touch you?

397
00:46:29,340 --> 00:46:31,140
You surely went an extra mile there.

398
00:46:33,130 --> 00:46:37,540
She only hugged and touched me. There was no kissing.

399
00:46:38,000 --> 00:46:39,900
Only you can do that to me.

400
00:46:41,300 --> 00:46:42,100
Really?

401
00:46:49,530 --> 00:46:50,330
Yes.

402
00:47:06,560 --> 00:47:14,900
Then, whatever marks she left on you…I’ll erase them all.

403
00:47:17,500 --> 00:47:18,700
How?

404
00:51:47,560 --> 00:51:48,940
Din…

405
00:52:05,060 --> 00:52:10,540
Once Uncle Thip is released from the hospital, I’ll ask him for his consent for our marriage.

406
00:52:11,940 --> 00:52:17,220
After that, we can pick up where we left off tonight.

407
00:52:21,130 --> 00:52:22,500
Until then, okay?

408
00:52:41,400 --> 00:52:50,500
I’m so lucky to have you, Lom, and Fai to always support me in everything.

409
00:53:41,300 --> 00:53:43,380
Rose and I will stay here for now then.

410
00:53:43,730 --> 00:53:46,660
Please take care of Uncle Thip and keep him safe.

411
00:53:49,260 --> 00:53:50,400
Thanks a lot, Lom.

412
00:53:58,260 --> 00:53:59,340
Let me help.

413
00:54:00,100 --> 00:54:01,060
Thank you.

414
00:54:06,600 --> 00:54:10,700
Lom is worried that Wasupol and his men might hold a grudge against us.

415
00:54:10,700 --> 00:54:12,780
She wants us to stay here for a while.

416
00:54:13,660 --> 00:54:15,930
What about Wasu, will he get arrested?

417
00:54:18,930 --> 00:54:21,730
I’m afraid he got away like before.

418
00:54:27,200 --> 00:54:29,600
Isn’t there any way to make these people pay for what they did?

419
00:54:35,700 --> 00:54:40,780
Rose, I know it’s unfair and you hate it.

420
00:54:41,760 --> 00:54:43,200
I feel the same way too.

421
00:54:45,200 --> 00:54:47,020
But we must not give up.

422
00:54:52,530 --> 00:54:53,980
Let’s keep fighting together.

423
00:54:56,380 --> 00:54:57,330
Yes.

424
00:55:04,300 --> 00:55:06,530
Let’s see, what did you cook for me?

425
00:55:12,460 --> 00:55:15,860
Hmm, so good!

426
00:55:16,960 --> 00:55:19,020
It’s just a plain toast.

427
00:55:20,460 --> 00:55:22,100
How’s the watermelon? Sweet?

428
00:55:22,860 --> 00:55:24,300
I’m about to try it.

429
00:55:42,000 --> 00:55:43,100
Is it sweet?

430
00:55:43,960 --> 00:55:46,340
Not sure yet. Can I try it again?

431
00:55:53,560 --> 00:55:54,980
Again.

432
00:56:04,930 --> 00:56:07,260
You dare show your face here?

433
00:56:07,460 --> 00:56:08,740
Do you have any idea what I had to go through yesterday?

434
00:56:08,740 --> 00:56:09,960
Mine wasn't any better than you.

435
00:56:10,460 --> 00:56:12,660
Miss Din already knew that I work for you.

436
00:56:13,300 --> 00:56:14,930
That’s why I got kicked out like a dog.

437
00:56:15,300 --> 00:56:16,540
Why are you telling me this?

438
00:56:18,100 --> 00:56:19,460
I have nowhere to go.

439
00:56:20,400 --> 00:56:24,060
Just admit it, that you’re useless now. Get lost!

440
00:56:25,360 --> 00:56:27,860
But I still have all information from Saen Rak farm.

441
00:56:30,000 --> 00:56:33,100
Have you forgotten that I’m the one whom Miss Din trusts the most?

442
00:56:34,660 --> 00:56:36,730
Don’t you want to get back at them, Mr. Wasu?

443
00:56:42,300 --> 00:56:46,500
What will you get for helping me? That brat won’t come back to you anyway.

444
00:56:49,860 --> 00:56:51,900
I want her life ruined.

445
00:57:04,560 --> 00:57:05,560
Yes, Moddang?

446
00:57:05,800 --> 00:57:11,700
[Moddang]: I have good news for you, Miss. Which one would you like to hear first? 1 or 2? 1 or 2?

447
00:57:11,700 --> 00:57:14,260
Enough with the nonsense. Cut to the chase now.

448
00:57:15,060 --> 00:57:16,700
[Moddang]: First is about Wasu’s case.

449
00:57:17,000 --> 00:57:20,060
Today, the police have summoned him for further interrogation.

450
00:57:20,130 --> 00:57:22,580
[Moddang]: I heard it’s because the last superintendent got sacked.

451
00:57:22,960 --> 00:57:27,400
[Moddang]: Miss Lom said he’s probably one of Mr. Wasupol’s co-conspirators.

452
00:57:29,000 --> 00:57:30,100
What’s the other news?

453
00:57:30,930 --> 00:57:36,940
[Moddang]: The doctor said Mr. Thipakorn’s condition is improving, so he’s allowed to move to a regular room, Miss.

454
00:57:38,130 --> 00:57:41,600
Really? I’ll go to the hospital right now.

455
00:57:45,300 --> 00:57:51,460
Din, Moddang just called. She said Dad is allowed to move out of the ICU.

456
00:57:52,580 --> 00:57:55,060
Can you please take me to the hospital?

457
00:57:55,500 --> 00:57:58,460
Aww, Moddang just stole my scene.

458
00:58:00,000 --> 00:58:02,900
You already knew? Why didn’t you tell me?

459
00:58:03,760 --> 00:58:07,740
Lom told me she’ll send someone to take us to the hospital.

460
00:58:07,740 --> 00:58:09,300
Then, we can go back to our farm.

461
00:58:09,860 --> 00:58:11,330
Is the situation safe now?

462
00:58:11,800 --> 00:58:17,060
To some extent, yes. Lom’s father has ordered the previous superintendent to be transferred to an inactive post.

463
00:58:18,500 --> 00:58:20,220
Lom’s father?

464
00:58:20,960 --> 00:58:24,300
Yes, Uncle Watid is a high-ranking police officer.

465
00:58:24,300 --> 00:58:28,260
Lom’s got evidence that this superintendent is corrupt. So, she asked for a little help from her father.

466
00:58:28,260 --> 00:58:31,620
He is now suspended and transferred for further investigation.

467
00:58:32,100 --> 00:58:34,420
This means Wasu has no one to help him anymore.

468
00:58:34,420 --> 00:58:37,620
The police are gathering evidence to arrest him.

469
00:58:48,800 --> 00:58:52,580
Please hang in there, Dad. You’ll be able to come home soon.

470
00:58:56,530 --> 00:59:00,580
Can you recall what happened that night?

471
00:59:17,060 --> 00:59:18,940
It wasn’t an accident, was it?

472
00:59:33,980 --> 00:59:38,500
Wa…su.

473
00:59:40,730 --> 00:59:43,900
You saw Wasu at the scene?

474
00:59:52,330 --> 00:59:56,860
This means…someone intentionally took the memory card from the dashcam.

475
00:59:58,940 --> 01:00:01,220
He wanted to destroy the evidence.

476
01:00:17,800 --> 01:00:18,940
Moddang.

477
01:00:21,530 --> 01:00:23,460
Miss Din and Miss Rose, you’re back!

478
01:00:28,530 --> 01:00:32,060
When you were away, I was so lonely, Miss.

479
01:00:33,730 --> 01:00:36,460
When I was away, was there anything unusual?

480
01:00:36,960 --> 01:00:37,940
No, Miss.

481
01:00:39,330 --> 01:00:41,700
Oh! Uncle Kla came to see you.

482
01:00:41,700 --> 01:00:45,500
But when he knew you weren’t back yet, he left an envelope for you instead.

483
01:00:45,500 --> 01:00:47,260
It’s probably in your room now.

484
01:01:13,400 --> 01:01:16,800
Looks like a clip from Wasu’s dashcam.

485
01:01:33,730 --> 01:01:36,740
This clip is the smoking gun. He won’t get away this time!

486
01:01:45,800 --> 01:01:47,780
[Kaew]: Miss Din will go to Chiang Mai tomorrow.

487
01:01:48,060 --> 01:01:50,340
And Lieutenant Wayo will not be at the farm.

488
01:01:51,130 --> 01:01:52,820
[Kaew]: We should hurry and get on with our plan.

489
01:01:53,620 --> 01:01:57,980
[Wasu]: That’s good. I’ll send someone to get rid of those bodyguards.

490
01:01:58,330 --> 01:02:01,980
What you have to do is use that brat to lure Rose out.

491
01:02:02,220 --> 01:02:06,860
Fine. But remember, don’t you dare lay a finger on Miss Din.

492
01:02:07,530 --> 01:02:08,940
Agreed.

493
01:02:09,260 --> 01:02:15,220
You can have that brat. As for Rose, she’s mine.

494
01:02:31,160 --> 01:02:33,460
Kaew sent us this evidence.

495
01:02:33,860 --> 01:02:37,220
The chance that you gave her is really not a waste.

496
01:02:41,300 --> 01:02:43,620
[Incoming call]

497
01:02:45,900 --> 01:02:46,760
Yes, Lom?

498
01:02:47,160 --> 01:02:51,780
Fah’s and my informants have got new evidence on human trafficking against Wasu and his gang.

499
01:02:51,780 --> 01:02:53,260
The police are now issuing an arrest warrant.

500
01:02:54,960 --> 01:02:58,660
I have new evidence too–a voice clip and photos of Wasu.

501
01:02:58,660 --> 01:03:00,380
I’ll send them to you now.

502
01:03:00,660 --> 01:03:04,100
Once the warrant is out, we can have him detained.

503
01:03:05,760 --> 01:03:07,760
And Kaew will be held as a material witness.

504
01:03:08,530 --> 01:03:11,620
All evidence points to him. He won’t get away this time.

505
01:03:13,160 --> 01:03:14,580
Thanks a lot, Lom.

506
01:03:20,700 --> 01:03:22,600
We’ll send them another big lot tonight.

507
01:03:23,700 --> 01:03:25,660
Tell our men to get ready.

508
01:03:26,660 --> 01:03:28,420
It’s risky but we have to do it.

509
01:03:28,960 --> 01:03:31,200
Otherwise, the big boss on that side will not spare us this time.

510
01:03:34,260 --> 01:03:35,620
Mr. Wasupol.

511
01:03:37,460 --> 01:03:40,380
We have an arrest warrant on you for human trafficking.

512
01:03:40,600 --> 01:03:42,820
Please come with us to the police station.

513
01:03:44,930 --> 01:03:45,820
Take him!

514
01:03:48,330 --> 01:03:49,180
Please.

515
01:03:58,900 --> 01:03:59,860
[Gunshots]

516
01:04:04,140 --> 01:04:05,180
This way, sir!

517
01:04:05,180 --> 01:04:07,060
Let’s go! Quick! Move!

518
01:04:07,060 --> 01:04:08,660
[Wasu]: Dad, get in the car!

519
01:04:08,660 --> 01:04:12,420
Let’s go! Move, move!

520
01:04:12,420 --> 01:04:13,540
[Wasu]: Hurry up!

521
01:04:15,420 --> 01:04:16,380
[Gunshots]

522
01:04:21,260 --> 01:04:22,980
Captain! Call for backups!

523
01:04:24,560 --> 01:04:25,620
Go after them!

524
01:04:28,800 --> 01:04:30,800
[Fai]: You bought a new flavour?
[Rose]: Mhm.

525
01:04:31,400 --> 01:04:32,620
Thanks, Lom.

526
01:04:35,700 --> 01:04:39,400
Lom said Wasupol and his son have escaped.

527
01:04:41,700 --> 01:04:43,730
Will they come here then?

528
01:04:45,730 --> 01:04:46,660
I don’t know too.

529
01:04:57,860 --> 01:04:59,160
Don’t worry, Rose.

530
01:04:59,500 --> 01:05:01,200
The police are tailing after them now.

531
01:05:03,700 --> 01:05:06,620
They’ve probably crossed the border by now.

532
01:05:06,620 --> 01:05:08,220
They won’t be coming back for sure.

533
01:05:08,560 --> 01:05:12,300
Who knows? I don’t think Wasu will accept his fate so easily.

534
01:05:29,660 --> 01:05:31,220
I’ll send you off here.

535
01:05:32,460 --> 01:05:34,200
What? What did you say?

536
01:05:34,730 --> 01:05:37,420
I’m not gonna run. I’ll go back to get my revenge.

537
01:05:37,560 --> 01:05:41,260
Are you out of your mind? Do you want to get arrested and thrown into jail?

538
01:05:42,060 --> 01:05:43,860
I won't let them live happily.

539
01:05:45,060 --> 01:05:46,700
I’m going to ruin their lives!

540
01:05:48,960 --> 01:05:51,580
Wasu! Wasu!

541
01:05:52,500 --> 01:05:53,740
We’d better hurry, sir.

542
01:06:18,960 --> 01:06:19,860
What’s the matter?

543
01:06:20,060 --> 01:06:23,460
Wasu and his father have escaped the police custody.

544
01:06:23,460 --> 01:06:27,020
Lieutenant Wayo wants us to take you to the safehouse for your safety.

545
01:06:31,500 --> 01:06:32,300
Okay.

546
01:06:32,400 --> 01:06:33,780
Then, please come…

547
01:06:47,860 --> 01:06:48,860
Wasu!

548
01:06:59,100 --> 01:07:02,060
Once the witness arrives at the safehouse, send someone to keep watch over her.

549
01:07:02,060 --> 01:07:02,860
Yes, sir.

550
01:07:04,500 --> 01:07:07,800
Lieutenant! Miss Kaew’s been abducted by Wasu and his men.

551
01:07:08,660 --> 01:07:09,420
Get the car.

552
01:07:09,420 --> 01:07:10,020
Yes, sir.

553
01:07:21,730 --> 01:07:23,500
[Bodyguard]: Hey, who’s that? Go check it out.

554
01:07:23,500 --> 01:07:24,620
[Bodyguard]: Okay.

555
01:07:25,100 --> 01:07:26,140
[Gunshots]

556
01:07:27,930 --> 01:07:28,730
Rose!

557
01:07:29,200 --> 01:07:30,500
- Fai!
- Get down.

558
01:07:30,560 --> 01:07:31,740
Miss Fai, Miss Din, Miss Rose!

559
01:07:31,740 --> 01:07:32,580
[Gunshots]

560
01:07:35,860 --> 01:07:39,740
[Moddang]: Miss Din, Miss Rose, Miss Fai! Wasu and his men are here now! Let’s run!

561
01:07:39,740 --> 01:07:41,020
Stay down!

562
01:07:41,200 --> 01:07:42,060
Sis!

563
01:07:52,700 --> 01:07:53,500
Let’s go!

564
01:07:53,940 --> 01:07:56,260
Let’s move! Go, go, go!

565
01:08:02,940 --> 01:08:06,700
[Incoming call from Lom]

566
01:08:36,529 --> 01:08:39,100
[Next Episode]
I’m so glad you’re safe, Kaew.

567
01:08:39,359 --> 01:08:41,800
I’ll move Dad to Bangkok for further treatment.

568
01:08:42,300 --> 01:08:44,300
I’ll go with you then.

569
01:08:44,300 --> 01:08:46,899
But can you please wait until I’ve resolved everything here?

570
01:08:46,930 --> 01:08:48,340
And when will that be?

571
01:08:49,600 --> 01:08:52,260
We both have weighty responsibilities on our hands right now.

572
01:08:52,260 --> 01:08:55,859
You have to look after the farm, and also Miss Kaew who’s still recovering.

573
01:08:55,859 --> 01:09:00,620
While we’re apart, I want you to take this time to revisit your own heart…

574
01:09:00,620 --> 01:09:05,180
whether this love we have will last long enough to be called ‘true love’.

575
01:09:05,819 --> 01:09:11,180
♫Forget about that promise and tell me honestly♫

576
01:09:11,540 --> 01:09:16,180
♫If you've ever loved me at all♫

577
01:09:30,979 --> 01:09:36,020
♫All the ups and downs we’ve been through together♫

578
01:09:36,020 --> 01:09:44,420
♫Those things made my heart begin to flutter♫

579
01:09:44,420 --> 01:09:49,740
♫Everytime when you look at me♫

580
01:09:49,740 --> 01:09:57,260
♫Do you know it makes me imagine things…so much ahead of myself?♫

581
01:09:57,260 --> 01:10:01,940
♫Always having you right by my side like that♫

582
01:10:01,940 --> 01:10:05,100
♫Do you also feel the same?♫

583
01:10:05,380 --> 01:10:14,140
♫I’m just curious and want to know♫

584
01:10:16,500 --> 01:10:20,260
♫Have you ever loved me?♫

585
01:10:20,260 --> 01:10:24,100
♫Please let me know♫

586
01:10:24,100 --> 01:10:30,460
♫If those hugs you gave me meant anything at all♫

587
01:10:30,460 --> 01:10:37,580
♫I don’t want to imagine it alone. Do you also feel the same?♫

588
01:10:37,580 --> 01:10:43,260
♫Forget about that promise and tell me honestly♫

589
01:10:43,260 --> 01:10:47,980
[Marriage on Earth]
♫If you’ve ever loved me at all♫
